n living systems needing to cope with complex environments or trying to\nefficiently coordinate themselves as an ensemble.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Tue, 16 Jul 2013 16:14:18 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Thu, 24 Jul 2014 15:54:46 GMT"}],"update_date":"2014-07-25"}
