ch can possibly affect the formation of\nplanets. Our model predictions are consistent with the range of observed masses\nand radii of proplyds in the Orion Nebula Cluster.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Tue, 16 Jul 2013 18:30:58 GMT"}],"update_date":"2015-06-16"}
