ical situations, the PE range\ncompensators would normally cause only marginal errors as compared to intrinsic\nuncertainties in treatment planning, patient setup, beam delivery, and clinical\nresponse.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Wed, 17 Jul 2013 06:10:54 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Fri, 30 Sep 2016 05:15:08 GMT"}],"update_date":"2016-10-03"}
