anical parts, the cooling of\nthe electronics, the readout, the data acquisition, the trigger, the monitoring\nand services.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Wed, 17 Jul 2013 09:07:39 GMT"}],"update_date":"2019-08-15"}
