onding to the precursor film with the fixed point\ncorresponding to the foot and then with the fixed point corresponding to the\nbath.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Wed, 17 Jul 2013 13:27:29 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Wed, 11 Sep 2013 13:46:36 GMT"},{"version":"v3","created":"Thu, 6 Feb 2014 13:15:03 GMT"}],"update_date":"2014-05-13"}
